      "description": "Sub-accounts under a merchant, each with their own Nomba Dedicated Virtual Account (DVA) for receiving payments. Created and managed with the master_api_key. Vendor API keys (scoped, generated here) are used for vendor-level operations like creating invoices and customers."
    },
